  "name": "Miconoide oblungo di Geo",
  "desc": "<p>A spore organism of some intelligence. It possesses extreme adaptability.</p><p>These shrooms' caps have hard outer layers derived from concretions of Geo energy. Its bodily structure is also quite likely to be denser than others of its kind.</p>",
